com.moandjiezana.uncommons.dbutils

Interface Converters


  • public interface Converters
    Groups Converters together. INSTANCE is a singleton that provides defaults and makes registered Converters available globally

    • Field Summary

      static Converters INSTANCE
      A singleton that provides defaults and makes registered Converters available globally.

    • Field Detail

      • INSTANCE

        static final Converters INSTANCE
        A singleton that provides defaults and makes registered Converters available globally. Supports all types returned by ResultSet#getXxx() methods, Instant and any class with a static valueOf(String) method. If no conversion can be performed, returns null.
